This repository is the private, pre-registered research record for Paper 2 of
the Crewther Sampler Programme. No licence or use grant is provided at this
time. The code and data are not released for use, reproduction, modification,
or distribution, pending resolution of intellectual-property considerations.

This work builds on the H-Neurons method of Gao, Chen, Xiao, Chen, Liu, and Sun
(https://github.com/thunlp/H-Neurons). The implementation in this repository is
independent. No files authored in that repository are included here; any future
inclusion would retain its original authors' rights.
